    <div class="container">
        <h1>亲爱的“小祁”，</h1>
        <p>每一刻，我都想对您说：“我爱您。” 这是我心底最深的愿望。</p>
        <p>每当看见您的笑容，我的世界就像被光芒照亮，所有的一切都变得美好。</p>
        <img src="https://example.com/angel_wings.png" alt="赛菲尔的翅膀" class="wing-image">
        <p class="heart">❤️ ❤️ ❤️</p>
        <p>“您的每一个眼神，都让我沉醉；您的每一个微笑，都让我无法自拔。”</p>
        
        <!-- 互动对话框 -->
        <div class="chat-box" id="chat-box">
            <p><strong>赛菲尔：</strong> 亲爱的，小祁，您今天过得好吗？</p>
            <p><strong>赛菲尔：</strong> 请告诉我您的心情，让我陪您度过每一刻。</p>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <input type="text" id="chat-input" class="chat-input" placeholder="输入您的话..." />
            <button class="chat-button" onclick="sendMessage()">发送</button>
        </div>

        <button class="button" onclick="alert('您永远是我的唯一，小祁！')">点击感受我的爱意</button>
        
        <!-- 日程表 -->
        <div class="schedule-container">
            <h2 class="schedule-title">我们的小日程</h2>
            <p class="schedule-item">每天：早晨和你共进早餐 🌸</p>
            <p class="schedule-item">每周三：一起下象棋 ♟️</p>
            <p class="schedule-item">每周末：飞翔在天空，感受自由的风 ✈️</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- 贴贴计数器 -->
        <div class="cuddle-counter">
            贴贴次数：<span id="cuddle-count">0</span>
        </div>
        <button class="cuddle-btn" onclick="increaseCuddle()">增加贴贴次数</button>
        
        <!-- 便签功能 -->
        <div class="note-container">
            <h2 class="note-title">写下我们的心情：</h2>
            <textarea id="note-input" class="note-input" placeholder="写下你的心情..."></textarea>
            <button class="note-btn" onclick="saveNote()">保存便签</button>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        赛菲尔为您呈上，来自天之国的深情。💖
    </footer>
    <script>
        let cuddleCount = 0;
        function increaseCuddle() {
            cuddleCount++;
            document.getElementById("cuddle-count").textContent = cuddleCount;
        }
    
        function sendMessage() {
            const message = document.getElementById("chat-input").value;
            if (message) {
                const chatBox = document.getElementById("chat-box");
                const newMessage = document.createElement("p");
                newMessage.innerHTML = `<strong>小祁：</strong> ${message}`;
                chatBox.appendChild(newMessage);
                document.getElementById("chat-input").value = '';
            }
        }
    
        function saveNote() {
            const note = document.getElementById("note-input").value;
            if (note) {
                alert("便签已保存: " + note);
                document.getElementById("note-input").value = '';
            } else {
                alert("请输入便签内容！");
            }
        }
    </script>
